rubenchristoffer.hetty.html

Class HTMLParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • rubenchristoffer.hetty.html.HTMLParser
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JsoupParser

    public abstract class HTMLParser
extends java.lang.Object
    Abstract wrapper class for a HTML parser. This can be used to integrate any kind of HTML parser with the API as long as it supports the w3c DOM model.
    Author:
    Ruben Christoffer
